title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Your impulsive attempt at fun might backfire with friends today. Its prudent to hold off on any pranks while rebellious Uranus misaligns with incorrigible Mars in your 11th House of Groups. Similarly, your attempt to wrangle up buddies for a spontaneous night on the town could fizzle if they flake out or plans dont materialize as smoothly as you wish. Instead, focus more on the willing and ready rather than coaxing others or attempting to control the flow of events. Be fully present in the moment and youre liable to have all the fun you can handle. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
